# Force LF line endings on checkout for files the build and tests
# compare byte-for-byte. Git's default `core.autocrlf=true` on Windows
# would otherwise rewrite committed LF to CRLF at checkout, breaking:
#
#   * Golden-file comparisons in test/integration/goldens/ — quicktype
#     emits LF on every platform; the goldens were generated with LF.
#   * API-snapshot drift detection in tool/api_snapshot.txt.
#
# Everything else stays on the repo default (Dart / Markdown / YAML
# round-trip fine under either convention).
test/integration/goldens/*.txt   text eol=lf
test/integration/goldens/*.json  text eol=lf
tool/api_snapshot.txt            text eol=lf
